 For any information, for registering, bug report,  suggestions  or  other,
 you can reach the author to the following address:

 Francesco Dipietromaria
 v. Genovesi, 15
 10128 Torino
 Italia

 ...or via E-mail to the following addresses:

 Fido:   2:334/21.26
 Amy:    39:101/402.26
 E-mail: dpm@sinet.it

 You can also have a look at my WWW home page:

 http://www.di.unito.it/pub/WWW/www_student/amiga/Dpm/

 I will not reply to snail mail because of postal expenses. It's better  to
 use e-mail.
@endnode

