@node "EasyFR 1 History" "EasyFR.guide/EasyFR 1.0 History"
@next "EasyFR 2.0 History"
@prev "History"
@{b} History@{ub}

 EasyFR 1.0:

 - First pubblic release (not distributed on internet beause english
 documantation were missing).
@endnode

@node "EasyFR 2.0 History" "EasyFR.guide/EasyFR 2.0 History"
@next "EasyFR 2.1 History"
@prev "EasyFR 1 History"
@{b} History@{ub}

 EasyFR 2.0:

 - The project comes in my hands (thanx to Angelo Vizzarro that give it to
   me);
 - Added traplist.library support;
 - Removed personal nodelist handling;
 - Added @{"XPKĀlibraries" link "XPK libraries" 0} support for reading packed filelist;

 Future developing of this software depend on your support.
@endnode

@node "EasyFR 2.1 History" "EasyFR.guide/EasyFR 2.1"
@next "EasyFR 2.2 History"
@prev "EasyFR 2.0 History"
@{b} EasyFR 2.1@{ub}


 - Plain filelist load function entirely rewritten: it's 40% faster!
 - "Sort by Date" function in InBound now sorts in decreasing mode.
 - New: "Sort by Lenght" sorting method added.
 - Added backup function (now works).
 - Added Scan Inbound function.
 - Added ASLFR_RejectIcons tag in the ASLRequest file for filelists
 - Now filename > 16 char can be added in the .REQ
 - Fixed the address dispaly (I hope): some times it prints "Į"
 - Now prints in addresses in 4D: if you insert "2:334/21" it prints
   "2:334/21.0"
 - EasyFR didn't save .REQ file when iconify. Fixed.
 - Every Allocation is now done using Memory Pools
 - If starting with a node without an associated filelist, it comes
   an error message (Could not open filelist). Fixed.
 - Added "Filelist Info" option from Project menu.
 - Added Iconify item in the Project menu.
 - Added a progress indicator & abort button for searching.
 - Added a Proceed & Cancel button to the Set Filenote window.
 - Added LZX support.
 - New menu "REQ List".
 - Added a Save entry in the REQ List menu.
 - Added Append Backup in the REQ List menu.
 - Added a full preconfiguration for first run.
 - Now you can call node with empty f'req list (usefull for multinode BBSes)
 - Catalog updated!

 Future releases of this software are related to your support.
@endnode

@node "EasyFR 2.2 History" "EasyFR.guide/EasyFR 2.2 History"
@next "Future"
@prev "EasyFR 2.1 History"
 EasyFR 2.2


 - Removed enforcer hit at startup
 - Added custom class for QuickList: now sorting works!
 - Added support for Bubble Help (MUI 3.x)
 - Added switch to Enable/Disable Bubble Help (only if using MUI 3.x)
 - Changed the About requester
 - Unregistered version pops up the about window for 15 seconds at startup
 - Added ReadArgs() if started from shell: FQFA/K,FILELIST
 - Added French catalogs (thanx to Florent Monteilhet)
 - Added Dutch catalogs (thanx to Raymond Penners)
@endnode

@node "Future" "EasyFR.guide/Futuro"
@next "Acknowledgements"
@prev "EasyFR 2.2 History"
 @{b}Future...@{ub}

 Future releases are planned to have some more feature:

 - A complete ARexx interface, able to pilot the program completely;
 - Make it possible to handle not in nodelist addresses using the QuickList
 (handling at least the phone number for the mailer);
 - Time cost calculation for the download of the selected files;
 - Other archivers;
 - MUI 3.1 new functions

 Suggestions are welcome.
@endnode

